<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <title>Your Verification Code</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .otp-container {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #007bff;
        letter-spacing: 5px;
      }
      .expiry {
        color: #6c757d;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Your Verification Code</h2>
    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>Please use the following {{subject}} to complete the process:</p>

    <div class='otp-container'>
      <div class='otp-code'>{{otp}}</div>
      <div class='expiry'>This code will expire in
        {{expiryMinutes}}
        minutes</div>
    </div>

    <p>If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email.</p>

    <p>Sincerely,<br />Saksham Jain<br />Founder, ProjexBio</p>
  </body>
</html>